-Pare down her powers to something more streamlined, rather than the current mishmash.

-Increase the emphasis on her vocal compulsive abilities.

-Make her more unfriendly, and very bitter. Have her bristle whenever a man orders her around, or when she sees a woman acting in a way she views as submissive towards a man.

-Make her not entirely rely on her compulsive abilities, but to be capable of manipulating people with ordinary communication. Have her enjoy doing so, especially to sow discord between lovers or friends.

-Tighten up her containment. If a mirror makes her easier to contain and more compliant, she can have one that's secured to the wall and covered with or made of something other than glass, so she can't break it and use shards for suicide or as weapons. Sixty meters square is ridiculous - five meters is far more reasonable, and the flowers are right out, except possibly as a reward for good behavior.

-Either get rid of the painting, or explain it as a portrait found among her possessions when she was brought into custody.

-If all else fails, don't delete it, -ARC it. She plays a not-insignificant role in the Clef-Kondraki incident story.

Edit: I seem to recall hearing that Kondraki is no longer around (and that some now consider him unwelcome for some reason). If indeed this article is orphaned, and nobody else steps up, I would be willing to attempt some fixes.





